Body:
with expected_protocol(ik.holzworth.HS9000, [':ATTACH?', ':CH1:FREQ?',
    ':CH1:FREQ:MIN?', ':CH1:FREQ:MAX?'], [':CH1:CH2:FOO', '1000 MHz',
    '100 MHz', '10 GHz'], sep='\n') as hs:
    channel = hs.channel[0]
    assert channel.frequency == 1 * u.GHz
    assert channel.frequency_min == 100 * u.MHz
    assert channel.frequency_max == 10 * u.GHz
